data("mtcars")
d1 = density(mtcars$cyl,from=0,to=100)
d2 = density(mtcars$mpg,from=0,to=100)
plot(d1,main="",xlab="")
lines(d2, col = "purple")

# points & text

points(mtcars$cyl,mtcars$mpg,pch="+")
text(6,22,": )")

# curve and polygon
f = function(x) return(1-exp(-x))
curve(f,2,4)
polygon(c(2.6,3.2,5.8,7.2),c(1,1,f(4.6),f(5.3)),col="red")

#箱式图

#标尺 scale
ggplot(small)+
  geom_point(aes(x=carat, y=price, shape=cut, colour=color))+
  scale_y_log10()+
  scale_colour_manual(values=rainbow(9))

# 统计变换（Statistics）
ggplot(small, aes(x=carat, y=price))+geom_point()+scale_y_log10()+stat_smooth()
## geom_smooth: method="auto" and size of largest group is >=1000, so using gam with formula: y ~ s(x, bs = "cs"). Use 'method = x' to change the smoothing method.
